<a href="http://mashable.com/2007/05/05/download-youtube-video/" rel="nofollow">Add YouTube Videos to Presentations</a>Â - free software to add YouTube, MySpace, and other videos to presentation.

There is nothing more powerful than a presentation which includes more than just plain text. The introduction and continuing improvements to thisÂ <a href="http://presentationsoft.about.com/od/powerpointtipsandfaqs/f/ppt_overview.htm" rel="nofollow">software</a>Â have changed the way people communicate. Creating a PowerPoint slideshow using all of its features conveys emotion and emphasis when you want to get make a point.[/fusion_text][separator style_type="single" top_margin="0" bottom_margin="20" sep_color="#cecece" icon="" width="" class="" id=""][fusion_text]<strong>Meeting Tomorrow</strong> provides organizations and businesses with such solutions as: <a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/projector-and-screen-rental">projectors and projector screenÂ rental</a>, <a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/flat-screen-monitor-rentals">monitor and display rentals</a>, and <a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/laptop-computer-rentals">laptop rental solutions</a>. We also rent <a href="http://meetingtomorrow.com/trade-show-kiosk-rentals">interactive kiosk solutions</a>.[/fusion_text][separator style_type="none" top_margin="" bottom_margin="20" sep_color="" icon="" width="" class="" id=""][/fullwidth]";s:10:"post_title";s:35:"A Guide to PowerPoint Presentations";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:35:"a-guide-to-powerpoint-presentations";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-09-30 21:41:17";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-09-30 21:41:17";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:1404;s:4:"guid";s:37:"http://mtstagingsite.com/?page_id=704";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}